{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbb310d9ad","title":"对棉粮工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9f1f07fd9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0061d0dd96","type":"title","text":"对棉粮工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"026e52b8c6","type":"paragraph","text":"必须把粮食抓紧，把棉花抓紧，把布匹抓紧，粮油征购工作不仅是一个经济任务，它首先是一个政治任务。一定要十分抓紧，每年一定要把收割、保管吃用（收、管、吃）抓得很紧，而且抓得及时。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"aa8d4be189","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意储备，铺张浪费，吃光用光，这些都是错误的，都是粮食工作中的资产阶级反动路线或者是资产阶级思想的反映","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"page":{"id":"53ed2fa5eb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad","start":450,"end":450}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"830722f71d","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意储备，铺张浪费，吃光用光，这些都是错误的，都是粮食工作中的资产阶级反动路线或者是资产阶级思想的反映。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"962b1d0eaa","type":"title","text":"对棉粮工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"c6199b6902","type":"paragraph","text":"必须把粮食抓紧，把棉花抓紧，把布匹抓紧，粮油征购工作不仅是一个经济任务，它首先是一个政治任务。一定要十分抓紧，每年一定要把收割、保管吃用（收、管、吃）抓的很紧，而且抓的及时。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"page":{"id":"06adc3fabe","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"bbb310d9ad","start":589,"end":58